[[File:Frankfurt Hauptwache Luminale.JPG|thumb|Light installation at [[Frankfurt]] luminale during Light + Building]]
'''Light + Building''' is a biennial architectural design and technology [[trade fair]] mainly focused on the fields of lighting, electrical engineering, building automation, and civil-engineering software. It is held at the [[Messe Frankfurt]] in [[Frankfurt am Main]], [[Germany]], and combined with the ''Luminale'' lighting design and art festival with installations and performances in and around the city.<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.faz.net/aktuell/rhein-main/die-stadt-in-licht-und-dunkel-luminale-in-frankfurt-12871913.html|title = Die Stadt in Licht und Dunkel|publisher = Frankfurter Allgemeine|accessdate = 2015-01-11}}</ref>
Light + Building is the world's largest trade fair in its industry. In 2018, there were 2,719 exhibitors and 220,864 visitors, over half of them from abroad. Top visitors besides Germany were coming from China, Italy, the Netherlands, France, Switzerland, the UK and Belgium, as well as from emerging markets like Russia, India, Finland, Korea and Ukraine.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.expobeds.com/event/light-building|title=Light + Building - Info - And - Stats|date=|df=}}</ref>
