'''Rubén Pacheco Lutz''' is a [[Costa Rica]]n businessman and former politician. Pacheco was the [[Political minister|minister]] of [[tourism]] from 2002-2006. In that position, Pacheco has emphazied "the country’s developed assets and stress the jungle less". Since leaving the government, Pacheco founded Enjoy Group Hotels & Resorts.

